defaulthands of those who might want to sell us gas at a very high price when we have to reduce our own access to energy supplies in Britain.
defaultNick Molhodefault: I think this overlooks the recent dynamics that we have been observing in the far east, in particular. As the International Energy Agency and the 
defaultPew
