defaultGareth Clubbdefault: We do have concerns about regulation, in relation to both the Welsh Government and National Resources Wales. Other than this one page, the Welsh Government have no planning guidance on onshore oil and gas. Out of all the thousands of pages of planning guidance that the Welsh Government have, that is the sum total of everything to do with shale gas and underground coal gasification.
