defaultWales
default and the Environment Agency Wales. Since 1 April, as one organisation, we have provided a single voice to respond to requests for planning advice. We have now put in place a work plan to develop that guidance further to reflect the purpose and remit of the new organisation. We will be working that up over the next few months.
